          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>red chilli relish</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until sticky and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>sticky ginger lean beef mince</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
