    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky ginger lean beef mince </strong>over the <strong>sesame noodles</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced red chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>reserved sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
